=== Self-Hosted Codegen ===
--- let x = 42 ---
0    | LoadInt 42
2    | StoreGlobal 0 (x)
5    | Return

--- let y = 1 + 2 * 3 ---
0    | LoadInt 1
2    | LoadInt 2
4    | LoadInt 3
6    | Mul
7    | Add
8    | StoreGlobal 0 (y)
11   | Return

--- fn double(x) = x * 2 ---
0    | MakeClosure proto=0
3    | StoreGlobal 0 (double)
6    | Return

--- fn add(a,b) = a + b  /  let r = add(1,2) ---
0    | MakeClosure proto=0
3    | StoreGlobal 0 (add)
6    | LoadGlobal 0 (add)
9    | LoadInt 1
11   | LoadInt 2
13   | Call argc=2
15   | StoreGlobal 1 (r)
18   | Return

--- 5 |> double ---
0    | LoadGlobal 0 (double)
3    | LoadInt 5
5    | Call argc=1
7    | Pop
8    | Return

--- if true 1 else 2 ---
0    | LoadBool 1
2    | JumpIfFalse +6
5    | Pop
6    | LoadInt 1
8    | Jump +3
11   | Pop
12   | LoadInt 2
14   | Pop
15   | Return

--- [1, 2, 3] ---
0    | LoadInt 1
2    | LoadInt 2
4    | LoadInt 3
6    | MakeList 3
9    | Pop
10   | Return

=== Lux compiles Lux ===
